  "official_title": "To amend the Comprehensive Environmental Response, Compensation, and Liability Act of 1980 to protect citizens, municipalities, and other generators and transporters of municipal solid waste and sewage sludge from lawsuits equating these substances with industrial hazardous wastes.", 
